  "texts": [
    "Taste is inherently shaped by culture, dietary habits, and social context, making it essential for models to incorporate diverse sensory data.",
    "Recent approaches address this challenge by including region-specific training data, embedding cultural descriptors, or using transfer learning to adapt models to underrepresented populations.",
    "These strategies help reduce prediction bias and support more equitable flavor personalization across global markets.",
    "These advancements reflect a broader trend in which AI tools are moving beyond theoretical modeling into tangible product development.",
    "Food companies now use AI not only to accelerate research and development but also to reduce costs and increase precision in sensory tuning."
  ],
